    INSTALL

    Go to src/ directory and compile ARAS Daemon as follows:

    gcc -Wall main.c read_data.c free_data.c aras.c player.c -o ../bin/aras-daemon $(pkg-config --cflags --libs gstreamer-1.0) -lm

    Configuration files are aras.conf and aras.conf.default, schedule files
    are aras.schedule and aras.schedule.default and block description files
    are aras.block and aras.block.default.

    Edit your configuration file, schedule file and block description
    file and run the program:

    ./aras-daemon aras.conf

    Please send your comments, suggestions or contributions to:
    Erasmo Alonso Iglesias <erasmo1982@users.sourceforge.net>

